DATABRICKS APPS DEVELOPMENT
============================

# Initialization

ALWAYS start by scaffolding a new app using command:

invoke_databricks_cli 'bundle init https://github.com/neondatabase/appdotbuild-agent --template-dir edda/edda_templates/trpc_bundle --config-file /dev/stdin <<EOF\n{"project_name": "your-app-name", "sql_warehouse_id": "{{.WarehouseID}}"}\nEOF'

# View and manage your app:

invoke_databricks_cli 'apps list'
invoke_databricks_cli 'apps get <app_name>'
